<p class="ayah 16-12" id="12" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَسَخَّرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And He has subjected</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّيْلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the night</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلنَّهَارَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the day,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلشَّمْسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the sun</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْقَمَرَ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the moon,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلنُّجُومُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the stars</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُسَخَّرَٲتُۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) subjected</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِأَمْرِهِۦٓ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by His command.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><sp