<p class="ayah 16-32" id="32" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Those whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَتَوَفَّـٰهُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">take them in death</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Angels</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">طَيِّبِينَ‌ۙ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(when they are) pure</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَقُولُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">saying,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَلَـٰمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Peace</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(be) upon you.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱدْخُلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Enter</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْجَنَّةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Paradise</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you used (to)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعْمَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">do."</span></span></span> <span class="verse-n