<p class="ayah 16-33" id="33" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَنظُرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they wait</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَأْتِيَهُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(should) come to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Angels</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَأْتِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(should) come</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Command</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّكَ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) your Lord?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Thus</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَعَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">did</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rt