<p class="ayah 16-89" id="89" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And the Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَبْعَثُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We will resurrect</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُمَّةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">nation</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَهِيدًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a witness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">over them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنفُسِهِمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">themselves.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَجِئْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And We (will) bring</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَهِيدًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) a witness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir