<p class="ayah 16-117" id="117" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَتَـٰعٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">An enjoyment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَلِيلٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">little</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) a punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلِيمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">painful.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>117<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
